data.description: Look no further...one owner,BRICK, one story on the corner in a cul-de-sac. Easy access to Paseo, schools, post office, shopping and medical. The location doesn't get any better! Fabulous curb appeal and landscaping. Mature trees and bushes give shade and beauty. Extra large patio cover for outside enjoyment. Great floor plan with a large kitchen open to family room with views of lush yard. Kitchen has island for easy preparation of meals. *Refrigerated air conditioning* 3 car garage and 3rd bay is a workshop with heater, cabinets, shelving and more although it can still be used as a garage if workshop is not needed. This home has been extremely well cared for.
